    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EVIL IS LUKRING</h2><br><strong>Spyrit Walker</strong> is a Survival Horror FPS set in a Weird Western world trapped in a perpetual night.<br><br>Grab your revolver and venture into the darkness, will you figure out the secrets of this world and grow strong enough to fight off EVIL?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/8f96a67653185cbb6ca09d2babccd440.poster.avif?t=1758699252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/8f96a67653185cbb6ca09d2babccd440.webm?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/8f96a67653185cbb6ca09d2babccd440.mp4?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Meet a strange cast of characters with their own quirks, powers and goals. You choose who to listen to and who to trust.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/cdc266e49fdddcb9c2edc01c4e641a67.poster.avif?t=1758699252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/cdc266e49fdddcb9c2edc01c4e641a67.webm?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/cdc266e49fdddcb9c2edc01c4e641a67.mp4?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Kick, shoot and explode your way through the legions of EVIL sent after you.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/0cf8169e74685a97b57e9ba40e404c77.poster.avif?t=1758699252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/0cf8169e74685a97b57e9ba40e404c77.webm?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/0cf8169e74685a97b57e9ba40e404c77.mp4?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>An open world full of secrets, explore in any order you want.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/63661cc05862ed39d53af7460f3e41c8.poster.avif?t=1758699252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/63661cc05862ed39d53af7460f3e41c8.webm?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/63661cc05862ed39d53af7460f3e41c8.mp4?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Multiple horrific creatures roam this land. Find their weaknesses to take them out for good.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/153c1ef169c865212478d91c1476e011.poster.avif?t=1758699252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/153c1ef169c865212478d91c1476e011.webm?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/153c1ef169c865212478d91c1476e011.mp4?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Find powerful weapons and abilities to gain an edge in combat and access new locations.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/615ca1ab7ae9408cf7901ff7d5348397.poster.avif?t=1758699252\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/615ca1ab7ae9408cf7901ff7d5348397.webm?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3032470/extras/615ca1ab7ae9408cf7901ff7d5348397.mp4?t=1758699252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Can you cleanse this land of EVIL, or is everything not as it seems?</strong>",
